CheapChronic.parse("today")

Everything is in future context and using localtime. Case is insensitive.

Other search terms:

today
tomorrow
yesterday

By Day:
monday-sunday
mon-sun

Additional syntax:

return the next day:
next <day>
this <day>
this coming <day>

return the next week:
next week

"in" syntax:
in <#> hours
in <#> days
in <#> weeks